ce:section.ce:para:
In addition to the keyword frequency analysis, the use of visual aids like tree maps (Fig. 7
                        ) and word clouds (Fig. 8
                        ) offers a more detailed and visually engaging exploration of the usage of these keywords during the bibliometric analysis. These visual representations help researchers and stakeholders gain a deeper understanding of the research landscape, trends, and the interconnectedness of various concepts within the field. Altogether, these keywords and visual tools collectively underscore the indispensable role of carbon-based nanomaterials in tackling heavy metal contamination and pollution in water, with a particular focus on the process of adsorption.
